# MERN-BookWorm
This app allows users to select great books from Google Books. They can keep a list of books they want to purchase.


# Description

Users must signup/login to explore books and save book searches. Their data is saved to the back end MongoDB.

This app features a React front end serving the client great books. The backend is a MongoDB database interfaced to GraphQL API built with Apollo Server. Node.js/Express.js powers the server.  

